--- !u!114 &872043992
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 872043991}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: fade6bde7ccbc9947be2401df74b5734, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  subtitleText: {fileID: 2023355591}
  backgroundPanel: {fileID: 0}
  normalFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8fc650701739faf46a8e64664ec66891, type: 2}
  highlightFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8583f08d08c314d309c3bdf643efc928, type: 2}
  normalColor: {r: 0.899371, g: 0.81301963, b: 0.4666547, a: 0.81960785}
  highlightColor: {r: 0.95, g: 0.1, b: 0.1, a: 1}
  highlightBold: 1
  highlightItalic: 0
  fadeInDuration: 0.2
  fadeOutDuration: 0.2
  autoPlay: 1
  entries:
  - label: Line 01
    text: Ahhhh
    startTime: 7
    duration: 1
  - label: Line 02
    text: Yes, I know. Let me go. Let me get out
    startTime: 18
    duration: 3
  - label: Line 03
    text: It is true. I have #loved you above everything else in the world.
    startTime: 30
    duration: 3
  - label: Line 04
    text: '#Torvald'
    startTime: 46
    duration: 2
  - label: Line 05
    text: Yes, now I am beginning to understand thoroughly
    startTime: 57
    duration: 4
  - label: Line 06
    text: Let me go. You shall not suffer for my sake.
    startTime: 100
    duration: 4
  - label: Line 07
    text: I am sorry Torvald I most go...
    startTime: 142
    duration: 3
  - label: Line 08
    text: ' I am #leaving you'
    startTime: 150
    duration: 3
  - label: Line 09
    text: You have never loved me. You have only thought it pleasant to be in love
      with me.
    startTime: 158
    duration: 3
  - label: Line 10
    text: I have been your doll-wife, just as at home I was papa's doll-child; and
      here the children have been my dolls.
    startTime: 162
    duration: 5
  - label: Line 11
    text: I thought it great fun when you played with me, just as they thought it
      great fun when I played with them. That is what our marriage has been, Torvald.
    startTime: 168
    duration: 6
  - label: Line 12
    text: Whose lessons? Mine, or the children's?
    startTime: 0
    duration: 1
  - label: Line 13
    text: Alas, Torvald, you are not the man to educate me into being a proper wife
      for you.
    startTime: 0
    duration: 3
  - label: Line 14
    text: I must #stand quite alone.
    startTime: 0
    duration: 2
  - label: Line 15
    text: I am going away from here now, at once.
    startTime: 0
    duration: 2
  - label: Line 16
    text: It is no use forbidding me anything any longer. I will take with me what
      belongs to #myself.
    startTime: 0
    duration: 3
  - label: 48
    text: I must try and get some sense, Torvald.
    startTime: 0
    duration: 2
  - label: Line 18
    text: I only know that it is necessary for me.
    startTime: 0
    duration: 2
  - label: Line 19
    text: My most #sacred #duties?
    startTime: 0
    duration: 2
  - label: Line 20
    text: I have other duties just as sacred.
    startTime: 0
    duration: 2
  - label: Line 21
    text: '#Good #bye, Torvald.'
    startTime: 0
    duration: 2
